title: Drawing, "End Table", ca. 1934–35
medium: Graphite on tracing paper, ruled border in graphite
markings: Stamp in black ink, lower right: DONALD DESKEY/501 MADISON AVENUE/NEW YORK CITY
inscribed: Inscribed in graphite at lower margin, right: SCALE 1 1/2"=1'0"/#/8283 [circled]/SUITE #8140 SUITE; dimensions in graphite
